high_descs: Walk forward until you hit a wall then turn right and walk a step until you are facing the toaster.
Pick up the knife on the edge of the counter.
Turn around and walk a step then turn left and walk until you are in front of the counter next to the garbage so you are facing it.
Cut the apple to the top left into three pieces.
Position yourself slightly to the right of where you are now facing the same direction.
Place the knife on top of the loaf of bread so it's leaning on it.
Move into the same spot you were in on step 3.
Pick up the bottom right piece of the apple.
Turn around and walk to the sink so you are facing it.
Cook the piece of apple in the microwave then take it back out and close the door.
Move back near where you got the apple on step 3 but slightly to the left so you are facing the garbage.
Put the piece of apple in the garbage.
anns.task_desc: Put a piece of cooked apple in the kitchen garbage.

high_descs: Move toward the fridge and turn left toward the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn right and walk towards the counter with a trash can next to it.
Cut the apple on the counter.
Turn right, take a step forward, and turn left to face the middle of the counter.
Place the knife on top of the loaf of bread on the counter.
Turn left, walk forward, and then face the apple on the counter.
Pick up the nearest apple slice.
Turn left, cross the room, then turn to the sink.
Open the microwave, put the apple inside, microwave it for seven seconds, wait, and open the microwave and take the apple out.
Turn left and walk to the trash can.
Put the apple slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Throw a microwaved apple slice in the trash.

high_descs: Turn right towards the sink.
Pick up the knife in the left side of the sink.
Turn around then turn left and walk to the small cupboard next to the stove.
Cut the apple on the counter into thirds.
Turn right then turn left and face the brown loaf of bread on the counter.
Put the knife on the loaf of bread.
Turn left the right to face the counter again.
Pick up an apple slice from the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink on your right.
Cook the apple in the microwave above the sink, then take the apple.
Turn right and walk to the gold trash can by the wall.
Put the apple in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooked apple slice in the trash.

high_descs: Go forward to the stove, go to the right to the counter where the toaster is.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter.
Turn around, go forward to the fridge, go to the left to the counter where the apple is.
Use the knife to cut the apple.
Turn to the right, move forward, turn to face the left where the bread is on the counter.
Put the butter knife down on top of the bread.
Turn to the left, move forward, turn to the right where the apple is on the counter.
Pick up a piece of the apple that is on the counter.
Turn around, go forward, hang a right and go to the microwave.
Put the apple inside the microwave and turn it on to cook, remove the apple when it is done cooking and close the microwave door.
Turn around, go forward, then hang a left and go to the garbage can.
Put the apple in the garbage can.
anns.task_desc: Put cooked apple in a garbage can.

high_descs: Turn right to the sink
Grab the knife by the sink
Turn right and walk to the end of the counter
Cut the fruit into three
Walk a little to the right
Put the knife on the pad on the right of the fruit
Walk a little to the left
Take a piece of the fruit
Turn around and walk straight and go to the sink on the right
Open the microwave on the top, put the piece of the fruit in the microwave, close the microwave and turn it on, take the fruit out when it's done, close the microwave
Turn right and walk straight to the trash bin
Throw the fruit into the trash bin
anns.task_desc: Cut the fruit, cook the fruit with microwave, throw it away into the trash bin

high_descs: Go to the counter on the left side of the sink.
Pick up the butter knife on the counter.
Turn and go to the end of the counter by the trash can.
Slice the apple on the counter.
Move over to the right away from the trash can.
Set the butter knife down on the plate.
Move left to the edge of the counter.
Pick up an apple slice on the counter.
Turn around and take a right at the fridge to the microwave.
Heat the apple slice in the microwave.
Take the hot apple slice across the room to the trash can.
Throw that hot apple slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple slice in the trash can.
